{"tid":956403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解八達通出咗咁多年啲人都只係當佢係一張交通卡","createTime":"2018-12-26T08:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T15:50:58.000Z","uid":227275,"like":28,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"aa22990d3d3576c9b3f4f76cccc9634d757cce70","tid":956403,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T08:39:06.000Z","msg":"去惠康百佳買嘢班師奶永遠都係用現金<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿婆阿伯更加唔洗講 只係識用嚟搭兩蚊車<br />\n明明8達通一嘟就可以畀到錢 班師奶就係都要慢慢咁搵散紙 散銀 曬撚曬大家啲時間<br />\n佢哋平時只會用張八達通黎坐車<br />\n亦都好明顯係香港社會進步唔到嘅原因之一<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係超級市場上面嗰啲自助付款機呢 <br />\n就永遠都唔見到有人用 <br />\n但係排隊用現金畀錢嘅就成堆人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都好嘅 咁我就唔使排隊可以直接畀錢走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問過佢哋點解咁鍾意比現金 聽過最on9既原因就係話 &rdquo; 我鍾意現兜兜畀錢嘅感覺 覺得實在啲&rdquo;  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccbfe2179064fb22c20b70f0213caa5e07269191","tid":956403,"uid":129506,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T08:43:52.000Z","msg":"自助機都多人用喎<br />\n<br />\n同m記一樣，啱啱出個機都冇人用，過一排就多"},{"pid":"c004935dff17c380556006cd470f02e7268d02dc","tid":956403,"uid":64781,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T08:45:48.000Z","msg":"買得多野要成日入錢又係煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用八達通自動增值啲c9又話怕信用卡公司收多佢錢/唔見八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95bb5e424b0fe1f0901af0fe428d6db005bee9a1","tid":956403,"uid":70183,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T08:46:40.000Z","msg":"琴日先串鳩個師奶<br />\n<br />\n去惠康買嘢<br />\n<br />\n扣八仔積分<br />\n<br />\n尾數又要比現金<br />\n<br />\n又八仔儲分<br />\n<br />\n屌你老尾做乜唔直接八仔比埋錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e7574129bf06ca065b424665b1294bc3441b710","tid":956403,"uid":174013,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T08:49:30.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲未識用自動增值既人<br />\n都唔知係咪住係山洞"},{"pid":"b4ea3beee5886ec88f22f42df0eafbace2b520e2","tid":956403,"uid":78533,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:17:52.000Z","msg":"一邊屌緊八達通食古不化　<br />\n你呢邊就屌香港人食古不化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但簡單Ｄ諗咪就係因為八達通做得唔全面<br />\n現金去到邊都比得　<br />\n八達通除左七仔超市同揸車外都唔知邊到用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b98173e289b3eac386dc71f45d54a811fc4e7a7","tid":956403,"uid":60378,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:19:45.000Z","msg":"慢慢妹下妹下唔覺駛得多錢 八達通用完增值覺得用好多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"540c9e49d2c854645d7af22c5170b1fd68bd15b0","tid":956403,"uid":184233,"like":13,"dislike":15,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:24:48.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆 我都係鍾意現兜兜比錢嘅感覺 覺得實在啲<br />\n<br />\n用卡比錢好無洗錢感覺 好易洗大咗 <br />\n現兜兜比錢就唔同 買襯野都會肉赤<br />\n變相慳咗錢"},{"pid":"86bd646b0e6e32be480a3245f50cfa3c83e6fb6d","tid":956403,"uid":5574,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:27:35.000Z","msg":"我香港有得八記就八記<br />\n有得applepay 就 applepay<br />\n八記做左自動轉賬, sofar 無出過事.<br />\n<br />\n日本就重方便, 電話有埋西瓜, 乜都用佢攪掂"},{"pid":"ccb09c774dea49f9726b3d308b17a4be5820853e","tid":956403,"uid":51250,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"86bd646b0e6e32be480a3245f50cfa3c83e6fb6d","tid":956403,"uid":5574,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:27:35.000Z","msg":"我香港有得八記就八記<br />\n有得applepay 就 applepay<br />\n八記做左自動轉賬, sofar 無出過事.<br />\n<br />\n日本就重方便, 電話有埋西瓜, 乜都用佢攪掂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:28:22.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢八記 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so